  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of Micardis® in Patients With Essential Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of Micardis® (Telmisartan) in Patients With Essential Hypertension</official_title>
